Before Maxima could reply to Blackstorm she turned her optics back to 
Sideways. The look on her face was none to sweet. "Optimus Prime ceased to function 
many eons ago." pausing. "Megatron no longer exists." she stated with some 
emotion in her voice, that of pain of the loss & anger. Eventhough Hydras now was 
a combination of Megatron & Galvatron... it was of the recent Megatron whom 
Maxima never met. Galvatron.. she didn't know if this was the same Galvatron she 
knew. 

"Your journey here has been a waste my friend." She smirked weakly. "Unless 
you wish too assist us?"

--part1_10d.24fde0f6.2c04ec7f_boundary
